PR<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"482be68613306eff95148ff598d7de9ddf5eb42a","tid":15314,"uid":3161,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T03:15:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>係咪好憎電視房既人</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n巴打 唔好skip 我"},{"pid":"e0c95b0e1277b13fcfc8c4e0c0bb4d47ba720cf8","tid":15314,"uid":37306,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T03:16:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>你本身有澳洲護照?<br />\n<br />\n香港人點先可以入職<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我係澳洲護照<br />\n上佢網站 遞CV 佢會講明邊d職位請本地人 邊d職位可以俾無居留既人做</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n無居留嘅人通常做咩位？<br />\n賭場會唔會擔保人留係度做之後拎PR<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n做餐飲部<br />\n我唔知 但應該唔會"},{"pid":"a6e7ee07b3ea97698d340e5065326024f7518dcd","tid":15314,"uid":37306,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T03:17:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>係咪好憎電視房既人</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n巴打 唔好skip 我</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nsor 睇漏你<br />\n唔係好明 電視房？"},{"pid":"824b283f66b84dea3766031cf00fbeecda96392d","tid":15314,"uid":31957,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T03:17:25.000Z","msg":"高額房d賭台有制改變結果?"},{"pid":"6116ae869ddc513acedd9144b198e1263055e0ab","tid":15314,"uid":352,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T03:18:42.000Z","msg":"巴打英文係咪好流利？"},{"pid":"b41a621b240df8b540194759656339bd6d74099e","tid":15314,"uid":37306,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T03:20:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>高額房d賭台有制改變結果?</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我唔係負責樓上既 <br />\n但相信無 因為根本就係十賭九輸 點解仲要出術？<br />\n而且一有人知 根本就唔係秘密 以後仲邊有人敢嚟玩？"},{"pid":"f3583313a033f7fd230d55521e7156615a4feee9","tid":15314,"uid":37306,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T03:21:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>巴打英文係咪好流利？</blockquote><br />\n<br 